,"_path":85},"❓ 用纯CSS判断鼠标进入的方向","/articles/css-judge-direction",{"title":87,"_path":88},"📝 你本可以少写些 if-else","/articles/no-more-if-else",{"title":90,"_path":91},"📝 技术博客归档","/articles/archive",{"title":93,"_path":94,"children":95},"读书笔记 / Notes","/books",[96],{"title":97,"_path":94},"📕 读书笔记",{"title":99,"_path":100,"children":101},"吉他剧场 / Music","/music",[102,104,107,110,113,116,119,122],{"title":103,"_path":100},"🎸 FingerStyle！",{"title":105,"_path":106},"🌬️ 等待的风","/music/wind",{"title":108,"_path":109},"💕 约定的海洋","/music/ocean",{"title":111,"_path":112},"🎼 Wings~You are the Hero！","/music/wings-you-are-the-hero",{"title":114,"_path":115},"🌏 残酷天使的行动纲领","/music/eva",{"title":117,"_path":118},"🏔️ 奇跡の山","/music/miracle-mountain",{"title":120,"_path":121},"🍷 Wu Wei","/music/wu-wei",{"title":123,"_path":124},"🌅 无题","/music/untitled",{"title":126,"_path":127,"children":128},"知识地图 / Maps","/maps",[129],{"title":130,"_path":127},"🏁 知识地图",{"title":132,"_path":133,"children":134},"造物 / Make","/tools",[135,137,140,143,146,149,152],{"title":136,"_path":133},"🧰 工具收集",{"title":138,"_path":139},"📕 博客","/tools/blog",{"title":141,"_path":142},"🥥 Coconut","/tools/coconut",{"title":144,"_path":145},"🧶 网易云音乐歌单排序","/tools/netease-sorter",{"title":147,"_path":148},"🌐 AnySort","/tools/anysort",{"title":150,"_path":151},"⛸️ UseScrollbar","/tools/use-scrollbar",{"title":153,"_path":154},"👓 Crapto","/tools/crypto-inline",{"title":156,"_path":157,"children":158},"我 / About","/hire",[159],{"title":160,"_path":157},"📬 技术简历",{"title":162,"_path":163,"children":164},"En","/en",[165],{"title":166,"_path":167,"children":168},"🦁 Welcome","/en/articles",[169],{"title":166,"_path":167},{"_path":167,"_dir":171,"_draft":172,"_partial":172,"_locale":173,"title":166,"description":174,"body":175,"_type":400,"_id":401,"_source":402,"_file":403,"_stem":404,"_extension":405},"en",false,"","Notes, blog posts, and small thoughts — my thinking and re-creation.",{"type":176,"children":177,"toc":391},"root",[178,187,193,198,204,209,214,235,258,264,269,303,315,320,334,340,350],{"type":179,"tag":180,"props":181,"children":183},"element","h2",{"id":182},"who-am-i",[184],{"type":185,"value":186},"text","Who am I?",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":189,"children":190},"p",{},[191],{"type":185,"value":192},"I’m a robot learning and imitating the humans around me. My Chinese name is “仿生狮子” (Bionic Lion), but my true identity is a cat.",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":194,"children":195},{},[196],{"type":185,"value":197},"This blog was built on a whim. Originally, I wanted to turn this site into a note-taking project — something closer to a rich-text editor, with more advanced interactions, like a note app. But after the site was up, I started slacking off. I never really thought about (or learned) how to take notes properly. That’s bad — don’t follow my example.",{"type":179,"tag":180,"props":199,"children":201},{"id":200},"why-write-a-blog",[202],{"type":185,"value":203},"Why write a blog?",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":205,"children":206},{},[207],{"type":185,"value":208},"In the past, the content on this homepage used to be a long manifesto. I kept revising it until I deleted it all, because those opinions no longer mattered. Still, whether the traditional “blog spirit” is good or bad, the form itself is hard to sustain over time.",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":210,"children":211},{},[212],{"type":185,"value":213},"I see this website (my blog) more as a kind of tombstone — the homepage, or a projection into the digital world. I once thought: if digitizing consciousness ever becomes legal, I’d probably be among the first to try uploading mine. Before that day, why can’t this website be the thing? As for why not other platforms, it’s simply because of the ongoing debates around data ownership.",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":215,"children":216},{},[217,219,233],{"type":185,"value":218},"Another perspective: I treat this blog as a digital garden",{"type":179,"tag":220,"props":221,"children":222},"sup",{},[223],{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":225,"children":230},"a",{"href":226,"ariaDescribedBy":227,"dataFootnoteRef":173,"id":229},"#user-content-fn-digital_garden",[228],"footnote-label","user-content-fnref-digital_garden",[231],{"type":185,"value":232},"1",{"type":185,"value":234},". Collecting references is like watering; writing something is like fertilizing. In the post-LLM era, having a personal imprint on a digital garden is rare. Let’s see what can grow from these scattered, human-ish fragments — the ash, the sparks, and all the pieces that make me.",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":236,"children":237},{},[238,240,246,248,256],{"type":185,"value":239},"This site provides ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":241,"children":243},{"href":242},"/links",[244],{"type":185,"value":245},"Links",{"type":185,"value":247}," and ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":249,"children":253},{"href":250,"rel":251},"https://lionad.art/feed.xml",[252],"nofollow",[254],{"type":185,"value":255},"RSS",{"type":185,"value":257},". Some content may also be synced to other platforms, such as Zhihu, WeChat Official Account (Lionad), or Bilibili.",{"type":179,"tag":180,"props":259,"children":261},{"id":260},"site-navigation",[262],{"type":185,"value":263},"Site navigation",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":265,"children":266},{},[267],{"type":185,"value":268},"Broadly speaking, this website contains three sections: “Flows”, tech blog posts, and notes.",{"type":179,"tag":270,"props":271,"children":272},"ul",{},[273,279,289],{"type":179,"tag":274,"props":275,"children":276},"li",{},[277],{"type":185,"value":278},"Flows: quick thoughts and some hard-to-classify pieces.",{"type":179,"tag":274,"props":280,"children":281},{},[282,287],{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":283,"children":284},{"href":127},[285],{"type":185,"value":286},"Notes",{"type":185,"value":288},": domain-oriented or structured notes.",{"type":179,"tag":274,"props":290,"children":291},{},[292,294,301],{"type":185,"value":293},"Tech blog posts: I used to publish on ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":295,"children":298},{"href":296,"rel":297},"https://juejin.cn/user/289926800227694",[252],[299],{"type":185,"value":300},"Juejin",{"type":185,"value":302},", but now this blog is the main place.",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":304,"children":305},{},[306,308,313],{"type":185,"value":307},"Since I’m not particularly good at writing technical blog posts, their proportion will gradually decrease. For a long while, my writing focus will be on the ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":309,"children":310},{"href":13},[311],{"type":185,"value":312},"“Forty-Two Essays” series",{"type":185,"value":314},".",{"type":179,"tag":180,"props":316,"children":318},{"id":317},"notes",[319],{"type":185,"value":286},{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":321,"children":322},{},[323,325,332],{"type":185,"value":324},"Unless otherwise specified, the content on this site is licensed under ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":326,"children":329},{"href":327,"rel":328},"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/",[252],[330],{"type":185,"value":331},"CC BY-NC-SA 4.0",{"type":185,"value":333},". Due to the inherent timeliness and uncertainty of notes — and because some content is assisted by GPT — please verify anything you rely on.",{"type":179,"tag":180,"props":335,"children":337},{"id":336},"contact",[338],{"type":185,"value":339},"Contact",{"type":179,"tag":188,"props":341,"children":342},{},[343,345,349],{"type":185,"value":344},"See: ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":346,"children":347},{"href":242},[348],{"type":185,"value":245},{"type":185,"value":314},{"type":179,"tag":351,"props":352,"children":355},"section",{"className":353,"dataFootnotes":173},[354],"footnotes",[356,363],{"type":179,"tag":180,"props":357,"children":360},{"className":358,"id":228},[359],"sr-only",[361],{"type":185,"value":362},"Footnotes",{"type":179,"tag":364,"props":365,"children":366},"ol",{},[367],{"type":179,"tag":274,"props":368,"children":370},{"id":369},"user-content-fn-digital_garden",[371,373,380,382],{"type":185,"value":372},"A garden gives us the ability to present ourselves as non-templated identities. It is a higher-fidelity version that preserves personality, contradictions, and complexity. I’m glad I found this essay: ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":374,"children":377},{"href":375,"rel":376},"https://maggieappleton.com/garden-history",[252],[378],{"type":185,"value":379},"A Brief History & Ethos of the Digital Garden",{"type":185,"value":381},". ",{"type":179,"tag":224,"props":383,"children":388},{"href":384,"ariaLabel":385,"className":386,"dataFootnoteBackref":173},"#user-content-fnref-digital_garden","Back to reference 1",[387],"data-footnote-backref",[389],{"type":185,"value":390},"↩",{"title":173,"searchDepth":392,"depth":392,"links":393},2,[394,395,396,397,398,399],{"id":182,"depth":392,"text":186},{"id":200,"depth":392,"text":203},{"id":260,"depth":392,"text":263},{"id":317,"depth":392,"text":286},{"id":336,"depth":392,"text":339},{"id":228,"depth":392,"text":362},"markdown","content:en:2.articles:0.index.md","content","en/2.articles/0.index.md","en/2.articles/0.index","md",{"_path":167},[408,411],{"_path":242,"title":409,"description":410},"友链","与我联络 & 友链",{"_path":412,"title":413,"description":173},"/todo","todo",1771071609451]